    Founded in 1994, Green Resource is one of the largest Turf & Ornamental and Erosion Control distributors in the Southeast

    About Us

    About Us

    Green Resource is a prominent distributor, of professional-grade fertilizer, chemicals, native and turfgrass seed, and erosion control products sold from six strategically-located warehouses. The company serves golf courses, lawn care operators, grounds maintenance companies, nurseries, retail lawn and garden centers, greenhouses, and prominent landscaping firms throughout the Southeast.

    It has been quite the journey ... but was made possible through our loyal customers and dedicated associates.

    Contact Us

    Field Sales Associate

    Join our team of dynamic field sales associates, whom drive sales through face-to-face customer engagement, sharing product knowledge, and suggestive selling.  Our sales professionals are experienced agronomic problem solvers who’s main tenet is to “serve” our customers to the best of their ability.

    Job Description

    Class 'A' CDL Driver

    As a part of our dedicated team, you will be delivering products to our customers. Drivers are responsible for safely unloading trucks equipped with a mobile forklift, in addition to working with teammates to enhance logistics and branch operations.

    Job Description

    Warehouse Personnel

    Our warehouse personnel receive and store products within the warehouse, prepare deliveries to job sites, and help maintain the overall organization of the branch.

    Job Description

    Counter Sales Associate

    Our counter sales associates are knowledgeable, energetic and consistently deliver the best overall customer experience. To succeed in this role, you need to be passionate and customer obsessed while serving commercial and residential consumers in the Green Industry.
